Dear <%= @user.fname %>,

Welcome to ICanLocalize.

To log-in to your new account, go to:
https://www.icanlocalize.com/login

Your login details are:
E-mail: <%= @user.email %>
Password: <%= @user.password %>

To start sending us content for translation, you need to allow WPML to access
your ICanLocalize account. To do this, log-in to your WordPress site and go to
WPML -> Translation Management -> Translation Services. There, click on
the "Authenticate" button and enter this key:

<%= @user.api_key %>

If you need any help, let us know. The best way to get help is from inside your
ICanLocalize account, by clicking on the "Get Help" tab.

Kind Regards,
ICanLocalize Team
